{"tid":246271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【等睇無事】行李藏違禁九節鞭 支那男今應訊","createTime":"2017-05-17T01:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T04:39:43.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"082d36bb8016aa46de5a8534f2e1b9c6d26df02d","tid":246271,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T01:10:08.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】警方於昨晚八時接報，指在香港國際機場準備乘飛機往外地，保安人員於安全檢查期間，在一名二十二歲支那男子的手提行李內，發現一支長約一點三五米的懷疑九節鞭，於是報案。警方經初步調查後，支那男子涉嫌攜帶違禁物品被捕。<br />\n<br />\n案件交由機場警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進。男子被控以一項攜帶違禁物品罪名，將於今日到西九龍裁判法院應訊。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲旅客切勿攜帶任何違禁物品。任何人若攜帶電槍等違禁物品抵達或離開香港，又或於香港過境，即屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/W9PGyez97hv4vYE1Vytkgw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTU4O2g9NDQ2O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170517a082441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FW9PGyez97hv4vYE1Vytkgw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTU4O2g9NDQ2O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170517a082441.jpg&h=f72b2efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E8%97%8F%E9%81%95%E7%A6%81%E4%B9%9D%E7%AF%80%E9%9E%AD-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7%E4%BB%8A%E6%87%89%E8%A8%8A-002300729.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2581%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25B9%259D%25E7%25AF%2580%25E9%259E%25AD-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%258A-002300729.html&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b911b20b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E8%97%8F%E9%81%95%E7%A6%81%E4%B9%9D%E7%AF%80%E9%9E%AD-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7%E4%BB%8A%E6%87%89%E8%A8%8A-002300729.html</a>"},{"pid":"8336dc55b62e41855f3437c1d13d45452bba4ec5","tid":246271,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":